title: Biscayne National Park: Trees and Shrubs
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Nature     Plants     Trees and Shrubs                Trees, Shrubs and Grasses         The Gumbo Limbo tree (Bursera simaruba) is also known as "the tourist tree".Â  Can you guess why? NPS  The following trees, shrubs, and grasses have been documented in the park. They have been sorted alphabetically by common name. The list is not exhaustive, and documented sightings of species not on this list are welcome. Submit your sightings to the webmaster.
